OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShirley Ballas nearly quit 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdancing due to bullying    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shirley Ballas has said bullying left  
OL,6, her on the verge of quitting dancing   
OL,7, just before Strictly Come Dancing asked
OL,8, her to join its judging panel.         
OL,10,FBallas said she was targeted by men "at
OL,11,Fthe top" while teaching dancers.       
OL,13,FThe 63 year old said couples she was   
OL,14,Ftraining were receiving "threats",     
OL,15,Fwarning their careers would be damaged 
OL,16,Fif they worked with Ballas.            
OL,18,FShe believes it was because of misogyny
OL,19,Fand the men involved "didn't want a    
OL,20,Fwoman in any high places".             
